column1: Table 2. Per Capita Personal Income, by Metropolitan Area, 2020–2022
1. Per capita personal income was computed using U.S. Census Bureau midyear population estimates for 2020 through 2022, released in March 2023.
Note. Metropolitan areas are defined (geographically delineated) by the Office of Management and Budget (OMB) Bulletin No. 20-01, issued March 6, 2020.
